<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Another night of Carabao Cup action brings another opportunity for a giant killing and none would be more shocking than if League One minnows Lincoln City could spring an upset against the Premier League champions Liverpool.</p>

<p>Jurgen Klopp's men have made a perfect start to the season but could rest some of their star players as they travel to the LNER Stadium tonight with a place in the fourth-round up for grabs.</p>

<p>Elsewhere, Manchester City will welcome Bournemouth while Aston Villa make the trip south to take on Bristol City.</p>

<p>Sportsmail are on hand to take you through all the action from Liverpool's game at Lincoln, plus bring you live score updates from the other two Carabao Cup third-round ties. </p>

<p>Host commentator</p>

<p>And welcome to tonight's Carabao Cup live blog. </p>

<p>We will be focusing on Lincoln vs Liverpool this evening, bringing you live coverage of the match, but that's not all with score updates from Manchester vs Bournemouth and Bristol City vs Aston Villa, which kicks off earlier in around half an hour's time.</p>

<p>We've got plenty to keep you occupied with before the action gets underway too so make sure you stick with us. </p>
